item.title: Clean and Smart Theme
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: The AccessPress Lite is clean and smart WordPress theme that look awesome throughout the multiple devices or screen resolution. It adapts automatically in your tablet and mobile phones. It's got several theme options which can be customize simply. It is the smart theme you will ever find for free.

item.title: Responsive Design
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Responsive website design is technique of developing websites which are hugely functional and the development that interact to user's behavior depending on screen sizes platform and orientation. It uses fluid grids, flexible images and a smart  usage of CSS media queries. Since the user switches from laptop to iPad, the responsive website automatically swap to accommodate for resolution, image size and scripting skills and consist technologies that automatically respond to user’s preferences.
